title: First American Music Awards Nominations Announced on "Good Morning America"
text:
First American Music Awards Nominations Announced on "Good Morning America" Posted just a moment ago 
Dick Clark Productions (NEW YORK) -- Singers Charlie Puth and Joe Jonas were on hand Tuesday on ABC's Good Morning America to announce the first group of nominees in six categories for this year's American Music Awards. The nominees are: 
FAVORITE ALBUM -- POP/ROCK Sam Smith, In the Lonely Hour Taylor Swift, 1989
